    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride and it's looking for a new home. It\u2019s been super reliable and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so you can just hop in and go. I've truly enjoyed driving this beauty, and I'd love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
