      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, which exemplifies a commitment to consistent maintenance and mechanical excellence. This model offers a refined driving experience, characterized by a well-preserved interior and a responsive powertrain that remains in commendable condition. For the discerning professional seeking a sophisticated balance of performance and value, this automobile represents an exceptional acquisition that meets our dealership\u2019s rigorous standards for quality and reliability.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
